<Author>Simmox3
<Content>never go anywhere else I have taken university art students to Berlin on numerous occasions and we always stay in either the Hotel Transit or the Transit Loft. I have never had a unpleasant experience. The staff are friendly and efficient, the rooms are basic, contemporary and clean, I haven't been in a hostel that compares with value for money and quality. The bar is open 24 hours and its in a brilliant location, with plenty of places to eat and drink with some local stores.I thoroughly recommend it. 
